⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The ETO
node 3BP · 3BP · ⟦The ETO:3BP:811f15⟧

WHO   — The ETO — humanity's traitor faith
WHAT  — The fifth column of the species: despair and worship organized into treason.
WHERE — 3BP · The Three-Body Problem  Framework inputs: Remembrance of Earth's Past (Liu Cixin, 2014-2016) + the Tencent (2023) & Netflix (2024) series; dual-agent web-verified  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the darkest idea in book one is that some of us would side with the hunters, and the ETO is that idea.
HOW   — By preparing Earth for conquest — Adventists for extinction, Redemptionists for salvation, Survivors for a bargain.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  We are the humans who looked at humanity and chose the other side. Some of us want you saved. Some of us want you gone. All of us opened the door.

